{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8931ef7f-13fc-422c-b534-ea5ccc3a09ab", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8931ef7f-13fc-422c-b534-ea5ccc3a09ab@3.pkg/1772597572146/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597572495", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8931ef7f-13fc-422c-b534-ea5ccc3a09ab@3.pkg/1772597572146/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597572495"}, "identifier": "8931ef7f-13fc-422c-b534-ea5ccc3a09ab", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>题干案例中，青少年群体通过民族团结实践传播正能量，高校青年以专业技能服务乡村振兴，两类群体均以实际行动诠释了青年与国家的共生关系：青年兴则国家兴，青年强则国家强，因此选B。A选项“都能”表述绝对化。C选项题干中两类青年均非传统意义的“专家”。题干中聚焦青年服务社会的行动，未涉及职业规划动机，D选项与题意无关。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>(原创)2024年7月，新疆学生穆妮热·阿布都万力与浙江学生吴沁霏因“书信手拉手”活动结成跨民族友谊，共同入选全国“新时代好少年”；同月，广东江门高校“百千万工程”突击队深入乡村，运用专业技能开展助农直播、中医药科普和墙绘创作。这些青年行动彰显了新时代的青春力量。可见（　　）</p>\n", "title": "(原创)2024年7月，新疆学生穆妮热·阿布都万力与浙江学生吴沁霏因“书信手拉手”活动结成跨民族友谊，共同入选全国“新时代好少年”；同月，广东江门高校“百千万工程”突击队深入乡村，运用专业技能开展助农直播、中医药科普和墙绘创作。这些青年行动彰显了新时代的青春力量。可见（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8931ef7f-13fc-422c-b534-ea5ccc3a09ab@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754842318534", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options